Name: 1) Average time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: 2) Total time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: 3) Minimum time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed after the execution of SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: 6) Time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer No Response
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response'

Name: 7) Average waiting time to SW-AE Assign Reviewers following SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: 8) Elapsed time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and the subsequent occurrence of Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: 9) Average time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Awaiting EIC Decision across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: 10) Minimum time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Agreed in variants containing multiple reviewer assignment attempts
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: 11) Total time it takes SW-AE Assign Reviewers after the execution of SW-Reviewer Selection is now due
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: 12) Cycle time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs within one week
Metric: the sum of the function base < 604800000 where base is the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: 13) Time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer Unavailable in high-latency variants
Metric: the sum of the function base > 604800000 where base is the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Reviewer Unavailable'

Name: 14) Average time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and the next SW-AE Assign Reviewers (reassignment duration)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: 15) Total time for SW-AE Assign Reviewers in variants that include Assign a Different Editor
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and the end of case where activity 'Assign a Different Editor occurs

Name: 16) Minimum time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: 17) Elapsed time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-EIC Major Revision in multi-round revision cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: 18) Average time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed after the last occurrence of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in a case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: 19) Time from the first SW-AE Assign Reviewers to the final SW-Reviewer Agreed in complex reviewer selection paths
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: 20) Total resolution time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in variants that result in manuscript acceptance versus rejection
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: 4) Average time for SW-AE Assign Reviewers grouped by case:concept:name
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': activity == 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'", 'end': '', 'aggregation': 'average', 'group_by': 'concept:name'}"
